{"tid":2154353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"與商會談美對港貨品標記新規定 邱騰華4時晤傳媒","createTime":"2020-08-13T05:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T08:43:07.000Z","uid":5195,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"b3d3519488aee1d40e7635b5995e3587263a38d0","tid":2154353,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:36:29.000Z","msg":"商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華今日與本地主要商會舉行會議，討論美國對香港貨品產地來源標記的新規定。邱騰華將於會後約下午4時，在政府總部地下演講廳會見傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普早前宣布終止香港的特殊待遇地位後，美國海關和邊境保護局公告，由9月25日起，所有由香港製造的進口商品，不可再標記「香港製造」（「Made in Hong Kong」）作為其來源，而必須標記「中國製造」（「Made in China」）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2441690eb026a7112fe4cdbfb8573af5fa3a3282","tid":2154353,"uid":66137,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:38:16.000Z","msg":"先準備定送飯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L34no8Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL34no8Z.png&h=9db23987&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bd3289cc7eaa8199e768eca8cd0eb51fe0cf5d1","tid":2154353,"uid":44171,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:39:20.000Z","msg":"邱局局長企硬，出口唔止貼MADE IN HK，加多張基本法賦予俾美國佬嘆吓"},{"pid":"76b74355e840ab128d03adb87c0ebea866571848","tid":2154353,"uid":322769,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:40:37.000Z","msg":"Made in China (Hong Kong) 囉"},{"pid":"60c2f56e8f8194b2f29cdf79e394275614c2fac4","tid":2154353,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bd3289cc7eaa8199e768eca8cd0eb51fe0cf5d1","tid":2154353,"uid":44171,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:39:20.000Z","msg":"邱局局長企硬，出口唔止貼MADE IN HK，加多張基本法賦予俾美國佬嘆吓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:40:41.000Z","msg":"加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b468df02a40876bd1a6888d6bd932c149d3e3f","tid":2154353,"uid":11316